flowchart LR
    accTitle: Read-only scope media inventory workflow
    accDescr: An author opens the Scope Media surface, which asks the local Docs service for a provider-independent inventory assembled from configuration, references, and registered stores.

    author["Author opens Scope Media with an active scope"] --> surface["Scope Media surface"]
    surface --> service["Local Docs service"]
    service --> inventory["Resolve scope configuration and document references"]
    inventory --> stores["List registered repository, external-local, and R2 locations"]
    stores --> evidence["Collect media identities and byte evidence"]
    evidence --> rows["Normalize items and missing references"]
    rows --> surface
    surface --> inspect["Filter, inspect, copy reference, or open item"]
